title: Genma Onimusha Rip.7z
description:
This is the original Xbox Release of Genma Onimusha. Seems hard to find this in working order at present time so I thought I would post up here. 

Tested working FTP to xbox, ASSUME it's working burned to disc also but not tested. Not my files either, just re-hosting for others to find.


Extract with 7zip, files already in .xbe format. FTP to xbox and play.

Enjoy.
